videos.description: Egor Koulechov gets the dime from Chris Chiozza and finishes in transition for Florida.
videos.headline: Florida's Koulechov finishes in transition with sweet reverse

videos.description: Jalen Hudson gets the breakaway slam as the Gators continue to blowout the Tide.
videos.headline: Hudson throws down the fast-break slam for Florida

videos.description: Donta Hall hits a falling-away one-handed shot for Alabama but was fouled before the shot.
videos.headline: Alabama's Hall hits crazy circus shot that doesn't count

videos.description: Lawson Schaffer provides a spark for Alabama, getting a steal and throwing the ball over his head to find Collin Sexton for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Alabama walk-on steals and delivers crazy pass to Sexton for score

videos.description: Jalen Hudson drives and tells Donta Hall to smile after putting him on a poster.
videos.headline: Hudson throws down emphatic slam on Alabama
